---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Home"
  description="Quiet The Mowers turns the #QuietTheMowers hashtag into local policy change. Sign a petition, start a campaign, measure noise, and reclaim quiet mornings."
>

<!-- Hero -->
<section class="section bg-gradient-to-b from-brand-50 to-white">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
      <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-brand-100 text-brand-800 rounded-full px-4 py-1.5 text-sm font-medium mb-8">
        <span class="relative flex h-2 w-2">
          <span class="animate-ping absolute inline-flex h-full w-full rounded-full bg-brand-400 opacity-75"></span>
          <span class="relative inline-flex rounded-full h-2 w-2 bg-brand-500"></span>
        </span>
        #QuietTheMowers Movement
      </div>

      <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-display font-bold text-brand-900 leading-tight mb-6">
        Reclaim Quiet<br />
        <span class="text-brand-600">Mornings.</span>
      </h1>

      <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-earth-600 mb-10 leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Gas-powered lawn equipment is loud, polluting, and unnecessary.
        We're building a movement of neighbors, organizers, and local leaders
        to make quiet mornings the norm &mdash; not the exception.
      </p>

      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4 mb-16">
        <a href="/campaigns" class="btn-primary text-lg px-8 py-4 w-full sm:w-auto">
          Find a Campaign
        </a>
        <a href="/manifesto" class="btn-secondary text-lg px-8 py-4 w-full sm:w-auto">
          Read the Manifesto
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mt-4">
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="text-3xl font-display font-bold text-brand-600">2,847</div>
          <div class="text-sm text-earth-500 mt-1">Total Signatures</div>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="text-3xl font-display font-bold text-brand-600">47</div>
          <div class="text-sm text-earth-500 mt-1">Active Campaigns</div>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="text-3xl font-display font-bold text-brand-600">12</div>
          <div class="text-sm text-earth-500 mt-1">Policy Wins</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Three Paths -->
<section class="section bg-white">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-display font-bold text-brand-900 mb-4">
        Three Ways to Join the Movement
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-earth-500 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Whether you have five minutes or want to lead a campaign, there's a place for you here.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <div class="bg-earth-50 rounded-2xl p-8 text-center">
        <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-brand-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-5">
          <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-brand-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 6.253v13m0-13C10.832 5.477 9.246 5 7.5 5S4.168 5.477 3 6.253v13C4.168 18.477 5.754 18 7.5 18s3.332.477 4.5 1.253m0-13C13.168 5.477 14.754 5 16.5 5c1.747 0 3.332.477 4.5 1.253v13C19.832 18.477 18.247 18 16.5 18c-1.746 0-3.332.477-4.5 1.253"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-display font-bold text-brand-900 mb-3">The Reader</h3>
        <p class="text-earth-600 mb-6">
          Land from the book or social media. Understand the movement, sign petitions, share posts. No account needed.
        </p>
        <a href="/manifesto" class="text-brand-600 font-semibold hover:text-brand-800 inline-flex items-center gap-1">
          Start Reading <span aria-hidden="true">&rarr;</span>
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-brand-50 rounded-2xl p-8 text-center border-2 border-brand-200">
        <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-brand-600 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-5">
          <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M11 5H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v11a2 2 0 002 2h11a2 2 0 002-2v-5m-1.414-9.414a2 2 0 112.828 2.828L11.828 15H9v-2.828l8.586-8.586z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-display font-bold text-brand-900 mb-3">The Organizer</h3>
        <p class="text-earth-600 mb-6">
          Start or run a local campaign. Build a petition, gather signatures, upload measurements, present to your HOA or city council.
        </p>
        <a href="/campaigns/new" class="btn-primary w-full">
          Start a Campaign
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-earth-50 rounded-2xl p-8 text-center">
        <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-accent-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-5">
          <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-accent-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17.657 18.657A8 8 0 016.343 7.343S7 9 9 10c0-2 .5-5 2.986-7C14 5 16.09 5.777 17.656 7.343A7.975 7.975 0 0120 13a7.975 7.975 0 01-2.343 5.657z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-display font-bold text-brand-900 mb-3">The Supporter</h3>
        <p class="text-earth-600 mb-6">
          Support existing campaigns, sign petitions, share your quiet lawn story, and cheer on your fellow organizers.
        </p>
        <a href="/wall" class="text-brand-600 font-semibold hover:text-brand-800 inline-flex items-center gap-1">
          See the Wall <span aria-hidden="true">&rarr;</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- The Problem -->
<section class="section bg-earth-50">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-display font-bold text-brand-900 mb-6">
          Gas Mowers Are Louder Than You Think
        </h2>
        <div class="prose">
          <ul class="space-y-4">
            <li class="flex gap-3">
              <span class="text-accent-500 font-bold shrink-0">85&ndash;95 dB</span>
              <span class="text-earth-700">Typical gas mower noise at the operator's ear &mdash; equivalent to a motorcycle at 25 feet. Hearing damage in under 2 hours.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-3">
              <span class="text-accent-500 font-bold shrink-0">300 ft</span>
              <span class="text-earth-700">Distance at which a gas leaf blower is still clearly audible inside a home with closed windows.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-3">
              <span class="text-accent-500 font-bold shrink-0">1 hr</span>
              <span class="text-earth-700">Running a gas mower for one hour produces the same smog-forming emissions as driving a car for 300 miles.</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <a href="/why" class="btn-secondary mt-6">
          See the Full Case
        </a>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-sm border border-earth-200">
        <div class="text-center">
          <p class="text-lg text-earth-500 italic mb-6">
            "I used to dread Saturday mornings. Now I wake up to birds &mdash; not blowers.
            Getting my HOA to ban gas equipment took 47 signatures and one council meeting."
          </p>
          <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-3">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-brand-100 flex items-center justify-center text-brand-700 font-bold text-sm">
              SK
            </div>
            <div class="text-left">
              <div class="font-semibold text-earth-900 text-sm">Sarah K.</div>
              <div class="text-earth-500 text-xs">Boulder, CO</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- How It Works -->
<section class="section bg-white">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-display font-bold text-brand-900 mb-4">
        How Change Happens
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-earth-500 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        The platform gives you everything you need, step by step.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
      {[
        { step: '1', title: 'Read & Learn', desc: 'Understand the issue. Read the manifesto, browse the ordinance library, see what other communities have done.' },
        { step: '2', title: 'Start or Join', desc: 'Find a campaign near you or start your own. Pick a template, set a goal, and tell your story.' },
        { step: '3', title: 'Measure & Document', desc: 'Rent or buy a sound meter. Upload real noise data to support your campaign with evidence, not just anecdotes.' },
        { step: '4', title: 'Show Up Prepared', desc: 'Walk into your HOA meeting or city council with a speaker card, 3-minute remarks, and a signature list.' },
      ].map(item => (
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-brand-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-xl font-bold mx-auto mb-4">
            {item.step}
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-display font-bold text-brand-900 mb-2">{item.title}</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-earth-500">{item.desc}</p>
        </div>
      ))}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Featured Testimonials -->
<section class="section bg-brand-50">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-display font-bold text-brand-900">
        First Quiet Mornings
      </h2>
      <a href="/wall" class="text-brand-600 font-semibold hover:text-brand-800 hidden sm:inline-flex items-center gap-1">
        See All Stories <span aria-hidden="true">&rarr;</span>
      </a>
    </div>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
      {[
        { quote: "I switched to electric and my neighbors thanked me. The difference is night and day.", author: "Mike R.", city: "Austin, TX", brand: "EGO" },
        { quote: "Never thought I'd care about lawn equipment. Then I had a baby who napped at 10 AM.", author: "Jennifer L.", city: "Portland, OR", brand: "Greenworks" },
        { quote: "Got my entire block to go electric. We have a group chat now. Saturday mornings are peaceful.", author: "David C.", city: "Denver, CO", brand: "Milwaukee" },
      ].map(t => (
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm border border-earth-200">
          <p class="text-earth-700 italic mb-4 leading-relaxed">&ldquo;{t.quote}&rdquo;</p>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <div class="w-9 h-9 rounded-full bg-accent-100 flex items-center justify-center text-accent-700 font-bold text-xs">
              {t.author.split(' ').map(n => n[0]).join('')}
            </div>
            <div>
              <div class="font-semibold text-earth-900 text-sm">{t.author}</div>
              <div class="text-earth-500 text-xs">{t.city} &middot; Switched to {t.brand}</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      ))}
    </div>
    <div class="text-center mt-8 sm:hidden">
      <a href="/wall" class="btn-secondary">
        See All Stories
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- The Tools -->
<section class="section bg-white">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-display font-bold text-brand-900 mb-4">
        Everything You Need
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-earth-500 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        The platform is the operational arm of the movement. The book sells the dream; the platform delivers the change.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
      {[
        { title: 'Petition Builder', desc: 'Pre-written templates for HOAs, city councils, and state legislation. Customize and launch in minutes.', href: '/campaigns/new' },
        { title: 'Sound Measurement', desc: 'Upload dB readings, audio clips, and photos. Rent a calibrated meter or use our protocol with your phone.', href: '/measure' },
        { title: 'Ordinance Library', desc: 'Searchable database of real noise and gas-equipment ordinances from cities and HOAs across the country.', href: '/ordinances' },
        { title: 'Council Meeting Prep', desc: 'Generate speaker cards, 3-minute remarks, and one-page handouts with your campaign data.', href: '/learn' },
        { title: 'Campaign Dashboard', desc: 'Track signatures, post updates, email your supporters, and manage your campaign from one place.', href: '/campaigns' },
        { title: 'Shareable Assets', desc: 'Yard signs, social media tiles, profile frames, and sample posts to spread the word.', href: '/share' },
      ].map(tool => (
        <a href={tool.href} class="block bg-earth-50 rounded-xl p-6 hover:bg-brand-50 hover:shadow-sm transition-all border border-transparent hover:border-brand-200">
          <h3 class="font-display font-bold text-brand-900 mb-2">{tool.title}</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-earth-500">{tool.desc}</p>
        </a>
      ))}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Final CTA -->
<section class="section bg-brand-900 text-white">
  <div class="container text-center">
    <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-display font-bold mb-6">
      Ready to Make Your Neighborhood Quieter?
    </h2>
    <p class="text-lg text-brand-200 mb-10 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
      Takes 5 minutes to sign a petition. Takes 15 minutes to start your own.
      Every signature moves the needle.
    </p>
    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4">
      <a href="/campaigns" class="btn-accent text-lg px-8 py-4">
        Find a Campaign
      </a>
      <a href="/campaigns/new" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-white/10 px-8 py-4 text-white font-semibold border border-white/20 hover:bg-white/20 transition-colors text-lg">
        Start a Campaign
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

</Layout>
